The paper discusses techniques for improving the quality of predictions made by deep neural networks, which is a common topic in machine learning research. The focus is on imposing constraints on the output of the network, which suggests that the paper is likely to be related to topics such as optimization (cs.LG), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), computer vision (cs.CV), neural networks (cs.NE), and natural language processing (cs.CL). Among these, cs.LG is the most likely category as it is the primary subfield of machine learning that deals with optimization techniques.
